msgid ""
"A higher FPS limit may result in smoother operation but may use more CPU/GPU resources.\n"
"Higher values may increase power usage, leading to reduced battery life on laptops."
msgstr ""
"较高的帧率可能带来更流畅的操作，但可能消耗更多 CPU/GPU 资源。\n"
"较高的数值可能增加功耗，导致笔记本电脑电池续航缩短。"

msgid ""
"FPS limit to use when window isn't focused to save CPU/GPU resources.\n"
"Lower values may help reducing power usage, but could increase response time when window is focused again."
msgstr ""
"窗口未聚焦时限制帧率，以节省 CPU/GPU 资源。\n"
"较低的数值可能有助于降低功耗，但可能增加窗口重新聚焦时的响应时间。"

msgid ""
